# Frontend Environment Variables - Configuration Guide

# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT
# Use: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# PRODUCTION (Vercel)
# Use: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://navin-portfolio.onrender.com
# OR your actual production backend URL

# To override these settings, create a .env.local file with:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=your_api_url_here
